avayaFabricAttachMib.name: avayaFabricAttachMib

revisions.description: Ver 18: Added avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientTable to support Zero Touch FA Client configuration.
Ver 17: Added avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementTrunkId attribute to export discovered element trunk associations.
Ver 16: Added autoPvidModeFaClient enumeration support for the avFabricAttachZeroTouchOptionFlags attribute.

Ver 15: Added avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemExpired, avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemDeleted and avFabricAttachStatsAsgnDeleted under AvFabricAttachStatsEntry. Also added avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemExpired, avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemDeleted and avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnDeleted Changes requested by Zuyan Wang (VSP) - Prem

Ver 14: Added values faClientOnaSdn(16) and faClientOnaSpbOIp(17) to avFabricAttachElementType and avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementType. Added values provisionModeDisabled(2), provisionModeSpbm(3) and provisionModeVlan(4) to avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementState. Changed avFabricAttachTimeout to avFabricAttachAsgnTimeout. Added mib objects avFabricAttachDiscTimeout, avFabricAttachPortMgmtIsid and avFabricAttachPortMgmtCvid. Changes requested by Zuyan Wang (VSP) - Prem
Ver 13: Added avFabricAttachExtendedLogging attribute to control extended logging capabilities. Added binding source attribute to the avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsTable.

Ver 12: Updated the avFabricAttachPortTable with per-port authentication attributes (avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthStatus, avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthKey). Updated discovered element authentication status enumerations. Updated statistics table object names by removing 'Sdk' to avoid confusion.
Ver 11: Added avFabricAttachTimeout, avFabricAttachSdkStatsTable, avFabricAttachGlobalSdkStats mib objects. Requested by Zuyan Wang for Fabric Attach on VSP8K (prempa).
Ver 9: Added Zero Touch attribute definitions. Updated FA Discovered Elements table.
Ver 8: Updated attribute enumerations and naming. Updated FA Discovered Elements table.
Ver 6: Updated FA element names in enumerations and object descriptions.
Ver 5: Added FA Discovered Elements table.
Ver 4: Added the ability to control host proxy operation. Expanded and clarified FA element types.
Ver 3: Added support for message authentication.
Ver 2: Added avFabricAttachPortTable and avFabricAttachAutoAttachService. Added RowStatus to IMPORTS.

avayaFabricAttachMib.description: This MIB module contains objects related to the Fabric Attach support.

avFabricAttachService.name: avFabricAttachService
avFabricAttachService.description: Exports the status of the Fabric Attach service.

avFabricAttachElementType.name: avFabricAttachElementType
avFabricAttachElementType.description: Exports the Fabric Attach element type indicating the services supported by the system. May be read-only on platforms that only support a single element type.

avFabricAttachPrimaryServerId.name: avFabricAttachPrimaryServerId
avFabricAttachPrimaryServerId.description: Exports primary server ID data on a FA Proxy if a primary server has been selected. A zero length string indicates that a primary server does not currently exist.

avFabricAttachPrimaryServerDescr.name: avFabricAttachPrimaryServerDescr
avFabricAttachPrimaryServerDescr.description: Exports a primary server description on a FA Proxy if a primary server has been selected.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsTable.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsTable
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsTable.description: This table contains the I-SID <--> VLAN assignments for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsEntry.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsEntry
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsEntry.description: Information about the I-SID <--> VLAN assignments for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsIfIndex.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsIfIndex
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsIfIndex.description: Interface identifier component of the I-SID <-> VLAN assignment.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsIsid.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsIsid
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsIsid.description: I-SID component of the I-SID <-> VLAN assignment.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsVlan.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsVlan
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsVlan.description: VLAN ID component of the I-SID <-> VLAN assignment.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsState.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsState
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsState.description: The current state of the Fabric Attach I-SID <-> VLAN assignment.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsRowStatus.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsRowStatus
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsRowStatus.description: This object allows entries to be created and deleted in the avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsTable.

avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsOrigin.name: avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsOrigin
avFabricAttachIsidVlanAsgnsOrigin.description: Origin information for the Fabric Attach I-SID <-> VLAN assignment.

avFabricAttachPortTable.name: avFabricAttachPortTable
avFabricAttachPortTable.description: This table contains port-specific data for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachPortEntry.name: avFabricAttachPortEntry
avFabricAttachPortEntry.description: Port-specific data related to the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachPortState.name: avFabricAttachPortState
avFabricAttachPortState.description: The current port state from a Fabric Attach perspective. Indicates whether FA TLVs will be included in LLDPDUs generated on the port (enabled) or not (disabled).

avFabricAttachPortRowStatus.name: avFabricAttachPortRowStatus
avFabricAttachPortRowStatus.description: This object allows entries to be created, deleted and modified in the avFabricAttachPortTable, if the operation is supported by the agent.

avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthStatus.name: avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthStatus
avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthStatus.description: Controls the current Fabric Attach message authentication status for the associated interface.

avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthKey.name: avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthKey
avFabricAttachPortMsgAuthKey.description: Provides access to the Fabric Attach message authentication key for the associated interface. Can be used to establish a new key of length 1..32 octets. Always returns a zero-length string when queried.

avFabricAttachPortMgmtIsid.name: avFabricAttachPortMgmtIsid
avFabricAttachPortMgmtIsid.description: Fabric Attach management i-sid for the associated interface. Zero means the management i-sid feature is not enabled

avFabricAttachPortMgmtCvid.name: avFabricAttachPortMgmtCvid
avFabricAttachPortMgmtCvid.description: Fabric Attach management customer vid for the associated interface. Zero means the management i-sid feature is not enabled. 4096 means it is untagged

avFabricAttachZeroTouchService.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchService
avFabricAttachZeroTouchService.description: Controls the status of the Fabric Attach Zero Touch service.

avFabricAttachMsgAuthStatus.name: avFabricAttachMsgAuthStatus
avFabricAttachMsgAuthStatus.description: Controls the current Fabric Attach message authentication status.

avFabricAttachMsgAuthKey.name: avFabricAttachMsgAuthKey
avFabricAttachMsgAuthKey.description: Provides access to the Fabric Attach message authentication key. Can be used to establish a new key of length 1..32 octets. Always returns a zero-length string when queried.

avFabricAttachClientProxyStatus.name: avFabricAttachClientProxyStatus
avFabricAttachClientProxyStatus.description: Controls the current Fabric Attach client proxy status. A FA Proxy provides proxy services to FA Clients only when client proxy support is enabled.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsTable.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsTable
avFabricAttachDiscElemsTable.description: This table contains details about locally connected Fabric Attach elements that have been discovered.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsEntry.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsEntry
avFabricAttachDiscElemsEntry.description: Contains details about a locally connected Fabric Attach element.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsIfIndex.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsIfIndex
avFabricAttachDiscElemsIfIndex.description: Identifies the interface through which the Fabric Attach element represented by this entry was discovered.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementType.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementType
avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementType.description: Identifies the Fabric Attach element type as advertised through LLDP.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementVlan.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementVlan
avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementVlan.description: Identifies the Fabric Attach element VLAN as advertised through LLDP.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementId.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementId
avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementId.description: Exports the Chassis ID associated with the discovered Fabric Attach element as advertised through LLDP.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementState.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementState
avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementState.description: Exports the state flag data associated with the discovered Fabric Attach element as advertised through LLDP.

avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementTrunkId.name: avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementTrunkId
avFabricAttachDiscElemsElementTrunkId.description: Identifies the trunk ID through which the Fabric Attach element represented by this entry was discovered.

avFabricAttachAutoProvision.name: avFabricAttachAutoProvision
avFabricAttachAutoProvision.description: Exports the Fabric Attach Auto Provision setting indicating the services supported by the system. May be read-only on platforms that don't support this functionality.

avFabricAttachProvisionMode.name: avFabricAttachProvisionMode
avFabricAttachProvisionMode.description: Exports the Fabric Attach provision mode.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchOptionFlags.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchOptionFlags
avFabricAttachZeroTouchOptionFlags.description: Exports the Zero Touch option data.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvTable.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvTable
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvTable.description: This table contains the Zero Touch NSV specifications for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvEntry.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvEntry
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvEntry.description: Information about the Zero Touch NSV specifications for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvType.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvType
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvType.description: Element type identifier component of the NSV specification.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvVlan.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvVlan
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvVlan.description: VLAN ID component of the NSV specification.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvPortPriority.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvPortPriority
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvPortPriority.description: Port priority component of the NSV specification.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvStateFlags.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvStateFlags
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvStateFlags.description: State flags associated with the NSV specification.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvRowStatus.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvRowStatus
avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvRowStatus.description: This object allows entries to be created and deleted in the avFabricAttachZeroTouchNsvTable.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusPriSrvrIpv4.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusPriSrvrIpv4Addr
avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusPriSrvrIpv4.description: This object represents the Zero Touch RADIUS primary server IPv4 address information currently maintained by the FA agent.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusSecSrvrIpv4.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusSecSrvrIpv4Addr
avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusSecSrvrIpv4.description: This object represents the Zero Touch RADIUS secondary server IPv4 address information currently maintained by the FA agent.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusTimeout.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusTimeout
avFabricAttachZeroTouchRadiusTimeout.description: This object represents the Zero Touch RADIUS timeout information currently maintained by the FA agent.

avFabricAttachStandaloneProxy.name: avFabricAttachStandaloneProxy
avFabricAttachStandaloneProxy.description: Controls the standalone FA Proxy mode.

avFabricAttachAsgnTimeout.name: avFabricAttachAsgnTimeout
avFabricAttachAsgnTimeout.description: Exports the Fabric Attach assignment timeout.

avFabricAttachStatsTable.name: avFabricAttachStatsTable
avFabricAttachStatsTable.description: This table contains information for all the SDK Fabric Attach statistics on a port

avFabricAttachStatsEntry.name: avFabricAttachStatsEntry
avFabricAttachStatsEntry.description: Entry contains statistics for the SDK of the Fabric Attach feature. Statistics are collected for a particular port.

avFabricAttachStatsPortIndex.name: avFabricAttachStatsPortIndex
avFabricAttachStatsPortIndex.description: An index value that uniquely identifies a port. This value is similar to ifIndex in MIB2.

avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemReceived.name: avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemReceived
avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemReceived.description: Indicates the number of discovery elements received for a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsAsgnReceived.name: avFabricAttachStatsAsgnReceived
avFabricAttachStatsAsgnReceived.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments received on a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsAsgnAccepted.name: avFabricAttachStatsAsgnAccepted
avFabricAttachStatsAsgnAccepted.description: Indicated the number of remote assignments accepted on a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsAsgnRejected.name: avFabricAttachStatsAsgnRejected
avFabricAttachStatsAsgnRejected.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments rejected on a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsAsgnExpired.name: avFabricAttachStatsAsgnExpired
avFabricAttachStatsAsgnExpired.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments that have expired on a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsAuthFailed.name: avFabricAttachStatsAuthFailed
avFabricAttachStatsAuthFailed.description: Indicates the number of authentication failed on a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemExpired.name: avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemExpired
avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemExpired.description: Indicates the number of discovery elements expired for a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemDeleted.name: avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemDeleted
avFabricAttachStatsDiscElemDeleted.description: Indicates the number of discovery elements deleted for a given port.

avFabricAttachStatsAsgnDeleted.name: avFabricAttachStatsAsgnDeleted
avFabricAttachStatsAsgnDeleted.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments that have been deleted on a given port.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemReceive.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemReceived
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemReceive.description: Indicates the number of discovery elements received.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnReceived.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnReceived
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnReceived.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments received.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnAccepted.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnAccepted
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnAccepted.description: Indicated the number of remote assignments accepted.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnRejected.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnRejected
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnRejected.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments rejected.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnExpired.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnExpired
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnExpired.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments that have expired.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAuthFailed.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAuthFailed
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAuthFailed.description: Indicates the number of authentication failed.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemExpired.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemExpired
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemExpired.description: Indicates the number of discovery elements expired.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemDeleted.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemDeleted
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsDiscElemDeleted.description: Indicates the number of discovery elements deleted.

avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnDeleted.name: avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnDeleted
avFabricAttachGlobalStatsAsgnDeleted.description: Indicates the number of remote assignments that have been deleted.

avFabricAttachExtendedLogging.name: avFabricAttachExtendedLogging
avFabricAttachExtendedLogging.description: Controls the Fabric Attach extended logging capabilities.

avFabricAttachDiscTimeout.name: avFabricAttachDiscTimeout
avFabricAttachDiscTimeout.description: Exports the Fabric Attach discovery timeout.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientTable.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientTable
avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientTable.description: This table contains the Zero Touch Client specifications for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientEntry.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientEntry
avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientEntry.description: Information about the Zero Touch Client specifications for the Fabric Attach application.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientType.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientType
avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientType.description: FA Element type identifier component of the Client specification.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientDescr.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientDescr
avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientDescr.description: Client description for the Client specification.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientOptionFlags.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientOptionFlags
avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientOptionFlags.description: Zero Touch options associated with the Client specification. Supported values are synchronized with the Zero Touch options available through the avFabricAttachZeroTouchOptionFlags attribute.

avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientRowStatus.name: avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientRowStatus
avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientRowStatus.description: This object allows entries to be created, deleted and modified in the avFabricAttachZeroTouchClientTable.
